Package: cogcache
Title: COG Tile Cache with Rust Decode
Version: 0.0.1.9010
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is a proof-of-concept for a Rust-native warper architecture,
 originally predicated on the goal of fetch and decode Cloud Optimized GeoTIFF
 tiles via HTTP range requests, with a Rust backend for decompression and
 predictor undo with tiles catalogued and cached in DuckDB.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc >= 1.65.0, xz
